      {
        "Id": "155520e9eb2642bcb48a109dc4b64b3f",
        "Title": "This script needs additional custom nodes from \r\n\r\nW:\\Toolbox NL projects\\000 Tekenafspraken\\DYNAMO\\MLA_scripts\\GIS\\MLA_CustomNode_Helpers \r\n\r\nand uses the materials \r\n\r\n00_MLA_Env_Buildings\r\n00_MLA_Env_Gray\r\n00_MLA_Env_Green\r\n00_MLA_Env_Blue\r\n\r\nAdditionally the pip packages \"ijson\" and \"numpy\" need to be installed once using this script:\r\n\r\nW:\\Toolbox NL projects\\000 Tekenafspraken\\DYNAMO\\MLA_scripts\\00_MLA_pipinstall.dyn \r\n\r\nLastly, in order to extract metadata, the following Project Parameters should be set for GenericModels:\r\n\r\nyear_of_construction -> Integer\r\ncadastre_id -> Text\r\nusage_status -> Text\r\nusage_type -> Text\r\n\r\nTo automatically create them you can use the script here:\r\n\r\nW:\\Toolbox NL projects\\000 Tekenafspraken\\DYNAMO\\MLA_scripts\\GIS\\V4\\MLA_GIS2BIM_CreateProjectParameters.dyn\r\n",
